@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Login Sistem

actor User
boundary "LoginScreen (Flutter)" as UI
control "AuthController (Laravel)" as API
database "Users Table" as DB
entity "SharedPrefs / LocalStorage" as Local

User -> UI : Input Email & Password
User -> UI : Klik Login
UI -> API : POST /api/login {email, password}
activate API
API -> DB : Check Credentials (Email)
activate DB
DB --> API : User Object & Hashed Password
deactivate DB

alt Sukses
    API -> API : Generate Sanctum Token
    API --> UI : JSON {token, user_data, success: true}
    UI -> Local : Save Token & Role
    UI -> User : Redirect to Dashboard (Owner/Tenant)
else Gagal
    API --> UI : JSON {message: 'Unauthorized', success: false}
    UI -> User : Tampilkan Pesan Error
end
deactivate API

@enduml
